  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the flat rice noodles with cold water and set aside.",
    "In a pot, bring chicken or vegetable broth to a boil. Add the rinsed rice noodles, garlic, and onion; reduce heat to low and simmer for about 20 minutes until tender.",
